### ── GAME SERVICE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET https://localhost:8443/api/game/health HTTP/1.1

### Start a match
POST https://localhost:8443/api/game/matches HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "player1_id": 1,
    "player2_id": 2
}

### Finish a match (replace 1 with the id returned above)
POST https://localhost:8443/api/game/matches/1/finish HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "winner_id": 1,
    "score_p1": 3,
    "score_p2": 0
}

### Get stats for a user
GET https://localhost:8443/api/game/stats/1 HTTP/1.1

### Get match history for a user
GET https://localhost:8443/api/game/matches/1 HTTP/1.1